{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Abolish antiquated rule to wait for a year to file for divorce",
        "additional_details": "I am having to wait months in order to file for divorce and release myself from this appalling situation. There are cases of domestic violence and other health & well-being issues that should allow people to file for divorce within the first year of marriage.",
        "background": "Abolish the antiquated rule that you must wait at least a year from the date of a marriage to file for divorce to allow people suffering from mental health or well-being issues to free themselves from an unhappy marriage.",
